extends java.lang.Object
implements org.joseki.server.SourceController, org.joseki.server.module.Loadable

Joseki SourceController for the D2R MAP. The Joseki-D2R SourceController allows you to use RDF models build with D2R MAP within the Joseki RDF Server. Joseki is a server for publishing RDF models on the web (see: http://www.joseki.org/). For details about installing Joseki and D2R MAP together see http://www.wiwiss.fu-berlin.de/suhl/bizer/d2rmap/usecases/joseki/HowTo-D2R4Joseki2.pdf
